items.sentence: Why didn't you tell me you didn't want my help?
Why didn't you tell me that you had to do that?
The sun disappeared slowly beneath the horizon.
There's a man at the gate who wants to see you.
Would it be OK if I sat on this bench with you?
I certainly hope that's what's going to happen.
I don't want to do that any more than Tom does.
This is Tom speaking. I'd like to speak to Ann.
When was the last time that you mowed the lawn?
Not having seen her before, I did not know her.
